EmailTemplate.subject: Save the date: Partnering for Success NAEP presentation event.
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Office Depot
Join us for a must-see presentation with the University of Missouri Extension.
WHAT
Learn how the University of Missouri Extension and Office Depot® created a best-in-class print and communications supply chain together.
WHEN
Monday, April 8, 1:35 pm–1:55 pm
WHERE
NAEP 98th Annual Meeting Kansas City Convention Center, 3501 B
Discover how the University of Missouri Extension partnered with Office Depot to:
• Transition its supply chain • Implement a new print-on-demand model with — Interactive digital publishing — Promotional products/apparel requirements • Deliver new efficiencies by integrating state-of-the-art technology from Office Depot into the Nexus@Mizzou platform • Establish MU Extension as a thought leader at land grant universities nationwide through a strategic partnership
We look forward to seeing you at this presentation hosted by Kyle Flinn from the University of Missouri Extension and Andrew Kniberg from Office Depot.
Office Depot is proud to be a 2019 NAEP Presidential Sponsor.
Come visit us at Booth #302 to charge your phone and win a prize!
